title: O'NEILL WETSUITS PSYCHOFREAK
description: The 2011 Psychofreak features three of O'Neill's new exclusive features. O'Neill's XDS-Air Firewall, new Triple XDS neoprene in the sleeves and shoulders, and the new SuperSeam Weld, which is 60% Thinner and Lighter than all other fluid seam welds. The Psychofreak also features Z.E.N. Zip Closure System, Minimal Seam Design, Seamless Paddle Zones, Krypto Knee Padz, and all new Super Seal cuffs.
